Add StarFive JH7110 SoC PCIe 2.0 PHY dt-binding.
PCIe PHY0 (phy@10210000) can be used as USB 3.0 PHY.

Signed-off-by: Minda Chen <minda.chen@starfivetech.com>
Reviewed-by: Hal Feng <hal.feng@starfivetech.com>
